{"tid":710778,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪地震電車停駛   人群徒步井然有序","createTime":"2018-06-21T04:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T11:44:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eeed8e4f4b533e4ec80c2001dfade846fde7b144","tid":710778,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180619/LA03/LA03_010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180619%2FLA03%2FLA03_010.jpg&h=a7a13b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本大阪昨強震，許多觀光客包括台灣遊客在內都心有餘悸，有人在睡夢中被搖醒，以為「作噩夢」，還有人前往機場時交通受阻。而當地的知名觀光景點環球影城緊急關閉多項遊樂設施進行安全檢查，並延後開園時間。<br />\n<br />\n昨強震導致地鐵和火車暫時停擺，有日本網友po照顯示，一列日本阪急電車的列車長，把車廂內整排座椅拆下來充當逃生梯，讓受困乘客能安全下車，不少台灣網友看了直呼「太強」，紛紛表示值得學習。電車停駛，通勤族只好沿著電車路線徒步。新淀川大橋上人潮密密麻麻，但又相當有秩序。<br />\n<br />\n來自美國的19歲女子吉派屈克首次到日本觀光，當時正在飯店睡覺，強震後驚恐不已，「超可怕，這是我第一次碰到地震，以為作噩夢。」她指，地震後飯店警鈴瞬間響起，並廣播要求房客遠離窗戶。<br />\n<br />\n儘管強震讓不少未曾經歷地震的旅客恐慌，但對日本人的鎮定與秩序卻也印象深刻。來自香港、在京都旅遊的陳姓女子便稱，儘管電車停駛造成車站滿是人，但「人人都在查看火車班次情況，日本人好平靜，好有秩序」。而一名昨從大阪返港的民眾說，當時正準備前往關西機場，突然強震，搖晃約20秒，前往機場的列車停駛，市區高速公路塞車。而一名昨出發前往大阪的香港民眾說，不會取消行程，「對日本建築物的防震設計有信心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180619/LA03/LA03_007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180619%2FLA03%2FLA03_007.jpg&h=ba1f26c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180619/LA03/LA03_008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180619%2FLA03%2FLA03_008.jpg&h=633f346c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20180619/LA03/LA03_009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20180619%2FLA03%2FLA03_009.jpg&h=af9534f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靜坐候車 在京都車站外，數百名日本學生靜靜坐著，等候新幹線重開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20180619/38047907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20180619%2F38047907&d=sezGOmjLrfSMKGOZkk38vIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=ea657c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20180619%2F38047907&h=d6a83fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20180619/38047907</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdff6e6999f8777a43dd36dd6d7404bdbb9da971","tid":710778,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c14866deb570094ce856777b4a52e47487f874","tid":710778,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdff6e6999f8777a43dd36dd6d7404bdbb9da971","tid":710778,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"咁打完風唔駛返工?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304f752d656c53a75989ef72c4a9968df73b1c4c","tid":710778,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdff6e6999f8777a43dd36dd6d7404bdbb9da971","tid":710778,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"地鐵壞車公司會叫你唔洗返工？"},{"pid":"111a47d6bfad0cfa775c0fb0ffc271b6b87813c4","tid":710778,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" clas